item.content:encoded:
Foodtycoon Frvr is a good managing game. Owning a coffee shop is every girl’s dream, now it comes true! You are mastering a little coffee shop, learn how to manage it, and how the shop keeps running well. I will teach you how to make drinks, with your level up you could make more kinds of drinks. Customers will get more and more, their Purchase demand is also more strange, but you have to satisfy them. You will get busier, improve your equipment to cook faster, you can also upgrade the materials that earn more money! Collect keys to unlock more characters!
Click to cook

item.content:encoded:
Today is Natalia’s father’s birthday. Natalia’s father has to go out to work during the day. Five-year-old Natalia and her mother want to prepare for Father’s Day surprises for their father during this time. Natalia decides to wash his father’s car, and then cook his favorite steak for his father. Natalia’s mother will make a birthday cake. They need to go out to buy some ingredients and tools for car washing, buy birthday gifts for dad by the way, and give gifts to dad at night.
Mouse click or tap to play.

item.content:encoded:
Taylor is a very well-behaved boy. Because the weather suddenly became very cold, Taylor had a fever. She couldn’t wear her favorite skirt. Her mother called the doctor. The doctor provided Taylor with some medicine and advice to make sure It can heal her within a few days. For Taylor, this is indeed a difficult time. She needs you now and you need to take care of Taylor until she recovers.
Mouse click or tap to play.

item.content:encoded:
Mathematics is one of the most complex subjects in the world. The Nobel Prize in Mathematics is awarded to those outstanding mathematics masters every year. Do you think you are good at mathematics? Math Fun Solarize is a math-related game that can test your math ability. You need to answer these math questions as soon as possible and check the scores you can get before you make a mistake. Smart kids are always good at doing math problems. If you want to exercise your calculation skills, you might as well try this game!
Mouse click or tap the screen to play.

item.content:encoded:
Monster Nail Doctor is a delicate doctor-themed game. Each one of these four creepy creatures has really been neglecting themselves lately. They could definitely use some monstrous manicures. Can you fix up their feet in this game for girls? Help them go from ghoulish to gorgeous! If you are a doctor-themed game lover, what are you waiting for? Come and experience this game, if you like it, don’t forget to share it with your friends.
Click to control.
